}, [dispatch]); // Calculate statistics const totalSlots = slots.length; const availableSlots = slots.filter(slot => slot.isAvailable).length; const occupiedSlots = totalSlots - availableSlots; const totalBookings = bookings.length; const today = new Date().toDateString(); return bookingDate === today; }); const todayBookings = todayBookingsArray.length; const totalRevenue = bookings .filter(booking => booking.status === 'COMPLETED') .reduce((sum, booking) => sum + parseFloat(booking.totalCost), 0); }); return distribution; }; const slotTypeDistribution = getSlotTypeDistribution(); const bookingStatusDistribution = getBookingStatusDistribution(); const getStatusColor = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'CONFIRMED': return 'bg-blue-100 text-blue-800';
